The evidence with the title 'Off base on sex ed - factcheck.org ' says Sep 10, 2008  ... Summary . A McCain-Palin campaign ad claims Obama's "one accomplishment" in the area of education was " legislation to teach comprehensive sex education' to kindergarteners . "But the claim is simply false, and it dates back to Alan Keyes' failed race against Obama for an open Senate seat in 2004 . 
